text:
Hello brother,

Kya hi bolu tere baare mein toh. Kya hi bakchodi machai hai tune. Initial years me teri image bahut hi different thi and end me aate aate bahut hi bakchod. Mujhe ache se yaad hai 3rd year me tu kya hi famous hua tha Synchro/Junoon ke wajah se. Tab bhai samaj aaya tha fest me bakchod banda aaya hain, bahut hi mast team banegi and bani bhi hain!! 

Bhai chaapa hain Online ANTARAGNI karwake, yeh tujhse obviously expected tha. Yeh last kuch saal bahut hi enthu me nikle kyoki koi saath me tha uss enthu ko samajne wala tha koi. 
Kabhi kabhi you meet someone and you start vibing wIth that person kyoki tum ek hi kaam kr rahe and saath me kaam kr krke tum dost ban jaate ho. Par in our case we bonded first after that we started working, and wohi reason hain ki we are "BHAI".

Ek baat bolunga....
Daaru bahut peeyi hai par asli maza yaaron ke saaath peene me hi aata hain. Daaru bass medium bann jaata hai baate krne ka. Jaldi hi peg banate hai yaar. Bhai bangalore aa jana mast plan banaaaye.

Tujhe saale bahut pareshan kiya hain and krte bhi rahunga. Par woh jo tujhe macchar kaata tha waise baate mat chupaya kr warna bahut bura hoga tere saath. 

Whenever in future you read this memoir I want you to call me and ask "how was our college life?", mein call pr jyada ache se yeh bata pauga. I am obviously not the one jo easily likh paaata hai, par mein bolkr jaroor bta sakta hu!!
BEHENCHOD abhi bhi padh raha hai "CALL KR" 

Love you brother <3
Cheers :)

Mere dost, mere bhai,

Kya hi likhu yaar tere baare mein. "Tu bhai hai mera". First year to 4th year kitni hi bakchodi kari hain. Bakchod group admin audition(we were the judges), photo ke saath mazak nahi, tere dressup hoke jaana date pe, basketball practice meri. Wing me bakchodiyon mein terese aage koi nahi hain bhai. Tune bahut hi pranks kare hain mere saath. 
Saath me 2nd year me double room se toh kitni hi kahaniyan start hui hain(it was the best thing that happened) and bahut hi pyaari dosti bhi. Ek kissa yaad aaya, apna ekdum se room saaf krna aur kuch constructive krne wala attitude. Phir uske kuch ghante baad hi room pr jo party hoti thi uska alag hi maza tha.
On that night on top of that water tank tu OAT se speaker dene aaya tha bhai.
I will always remember that A5 wing party final night moment, I don't know ki tujhe yaad hai yaa nahi. Par mere liye woh bahut  memorable moment tha bhai. Bangalore mein toh saath hain hi apan aur kisse banenge hi bhai. Milte hai jaldi mere dost.
Love you brother. 
- Your roomie
